<emphasis id="B938EAE3BB7EFFFBFE8EEA63FD84F8A5" box="[329,526,1865,1888]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="556">Melanophora chia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A20B5798BB7EFFFBFDD3EA63FDEDF8A5" box="[532,615,1865,1888]" pageId="4" pageNumber="556" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
<emphasis id="B938EAE3BB7EFFFBFDABEA62FD0AF8A5" bold="true" box="[620,640,1864,1888]" pageId="4" pageNumber="556">2.</emphasis>
Head in lateral view (♂, holotype), scale bar: 0.5 mm. 
<emphasis id="B938EAE3BB7EFFFBFB0CEA62FB54F8A5" bold="true" box="[1227,1246,1864,1888]" pageId="4" pageNumber="556">3.</emphasis>
