Back of head and anterior third of thorax in lateral view (♀, paratype), scale bar: 0.3 mm. 
<emphasis id="B938EAE3BB7EFFFBFBB9EABAFB18F86D" bold="true" box="[1150,1170,1936,1960]" pageId="4" pageNumber="556">6.</emphasis>
