<emphasis id="B938EAE3BB7EFFFBFD81EA9EFDD0F809" bold="true" box="[582,602,1972,1996]" pageId="4" pageNumber="556">7.</emphasis>
Left metathoracic spiracle (♀, paratype), scale bar: 0.1 mm. 
<emphasis id="B938EAE3BB7EFFFBFB30EA9EFA86F809" bold="true" box="[1271,1292,1972,1996]" pageId="4" pageNumber="556">8.</emphasis>
Scutellum in laterodorsal view (♂, holotype), scale bar: 0.5 mm.
</paragraph>
